529
00:38:09,600 --> 00:38:11,000
If we can cast doubt on 30% of them,

530
00:38:11,000 --> 00:38:13,700
we can defend for another two to four hours.

531
00:38:13,700 --> 00:38:14,600
Okay.

532
00:38:14,600 --> 00:38:16,100
Thank you.

533
00:38:58,400 --> 00:39:00,400
