535
00:39:02,500 --> 00:39:06,100
We might not be able to last till tomorrow.

536
00:39:06,900 --> 00:39:08,900
I need to figure out a solution.

537
00:39:28,400 --> 00:39:30,000
Director Bai.

538
00:39:33,400 --> 00:39:34,900
Commander Feng.

539
